This paper deals with the use of deep learning techniques for skin lesion segmentation and classification, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of artificial data augmentation techniques, which is a common topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper involves the use of image processing techniques, which is a topic in multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
